% MCD GreenRoots - Mocodo source (https://mocodo.net)
% CONCEPTUAL level (Merise) - reverse-engineered from the Prisma schema.
% Names kept in ENGLISH to stay aligned with the codebase (traceability MCD -> schema).
% Stock rule: Option A -> stockQuantity/lowStockThreshold are attributes of Tree at the
% MCD level; the TreeStock table (vertical partitioning) only appears at the MLD level.
% Technical attributes (security tokens, timestamps, paymentIntentId...) are deliberately
% left out of the MCD and reintroduced at the MPD level.

Role: id, name
HAS, 11 User, 0N Role
User: id, email, password, firstName, lastName, avatarUrl, isEmailVerified

PLACES, 0N User, 11 Order
Order: id, totalAmount, totalExclTax, totalVatAmount, currency, contactEmail, invoiceNumber, invoiceDate, paymentStatus, orderStatus

CONTAINS, 1N Order, 0N Tree: quantity, unitPrice, vatRate
HAS_ADDRESS, 1N Order, 11 OrderAddress
OrderAddress: id, type, firstName, lastName, street, streetLine2, postalCode, city, countryCode, phone

Tree: id, name, scientificName, description, imageUrl, price, heightMax, stockQuantity, lowStockThreshold
BELONGS_TO, 11 Tree, 0N Category
Category: id, name

PLANTED_AT, 11 Tree, 0N Location
Location: id, name, region, coordinates, description, imageUrl
LOCATED_IN, 11 Location, 0N Country
Country: id, code, name, currency, isBillingAvailable, isPlantingAvailable
